\id JAS  
\ide UTF8
\h JAMES 
\toc1 Babior Le Ye Budoh Mo Irel JAMES 
\toc2 James 
\toc3 Jas 
\mt1 JAMES  
\is1 Hamadefal  
\ip \add Babior le ye budoh mo irel\add* \bk James\bk* ila sew babiorol folol hammal le ye teftaf bo ye be loh “irer panger mokwe lol Deus le resa yeregloh lal faileng le.” Yeramtala tefayal babior le, ila ye teptap hapatpat kala ye ffod irel yal hamdefa kofael wululul repiy mo igeger mo wegdigir Kristiano. Iwe ngo yesa chapiy mo irel igegel Kristiano ngo yesa hamdefa meka mmaler yarmat mo yar hafohoy, mo luluwal ka ye ma hasgichloh luwul molfid, mo wegdeg ka ye momay, hafobder, tugulul ladep mo wegdeg, iwe mo irel yach ma tapeli meka yewach irel hapatpat mo irel yach ma happaliyel fengal, iwe mo hattodah mo yach ma hatetalogich, mo yach ma salepa kapter sibis mo yach ma habos, mo lelayel repiyach mo mepel.  
\ip Mala babior le ye hakkela le ye palleng pelal, ila kofal yach wegdeg le yebe fidfid ngal yach tugulul ladep, irel yach dabey mele wululul Kristiano.  
\is1 Palpal Meka Yadol Babior Le  
\io1 Hamadefal \ior 1:1\ior*  
\io1 Tugulul ladep mo repiy \ior 1:2–8\ior*  
\io1 Hafohoy mo mmal \ior 1:9–11\ior*  
\io1 Hagilgil mo wegwegel ladep \ior 1:12–18\ior*  
\io1 Yach ma rongrong mo yach ma foru \ior 1:19–27\ior*  
\io1 Sibe llugu depach bo side harere \ior 2:1–13\ior*  
\io1 Yengang mo tugulul ladep \ior 2:14–26\ior*  
\io1 Kristiano mo hapatpat kala yar \ior 3:1–18\ior*  
\io1 Kristiano mo faileng le \ior 4:1—5:6\ior*  
\io1 Samat mo samat foloy mo hamedaf \ior 5:7–20\ior*  
\c 1  
\s1 Babior Le Ye Budoh Mo Irel  
\p
\v 1 Babior le ila ye budoh mo irel James le iy semal boy le lol Deus mo Samol Jesus Kristus:  
\p Yai habong ngalir panger mekla lol Deus le re medardar fedal lal ballel faileng le.\x - \xo 1:1 \xt Mt 13:55; Mk 6:3; Ac 15:13; Ga 1:19\x*   
\s1 Tugulul Ladep Mo Repiy  
\p
\v 2 Hami re wol bisiy, habe itol lal dipmi le hami ila ha yolbuw irel yodka be holahmi pangal metmetael weres iyang,  
\v 3 bo ha gola le be kkel chog yami tugul luwul yami weres mo hafohoy, ila ngo yebe kawraloh le te tugul mele iy, ngo be yoh ngalugmi le habe yedamgel iyang.  
\v 4 Habe itol dipmi irel yami yedamgel ngo ha towe ppoloh yee, yela hola yodla iy, ila ngo towe yor hapagol yami mel ngo tor mele towe yoh ngalugmi.  
\v 5 Semal le ye temedaf ngo sa mepel ngal Deus bo yebe fang ngali teram. Bo Deus ila ye mmol ngo ye momay yal hagiyeg ngal pangal yarmat.  
\v 6 Ha towe yeyewal. Ha hatugulu lal dipmi irel yami mapel bo semal le yebe te tugul lal depal, ngo yebe wochog hatobtob le yema dabey felel yaeng.  
\v 7-8 Tappel rechoka te tugul lal deper ngo re yeyewal irel pangal mekla rema foru, ila re towe luluwaley le be yor mele Samol yebe fang ngalir.   
\s1 Hafohoy Mo Mmal  
\p
\v 9 Kristiano ka re hafohoy ila be momay deper irel yodla Deus be hatagitardah.  
\v 10 Ngo Kristiano ka re mmal ila rebe rraey irel mala Deus be hatetalordiy. Rechokla re mmal ila rebe torloh le rebe wochog floresal ire ka ye tumuldah chog.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1:10–11; Is 40:6–7 (LXX)\x*  
\v 11 Yebe kkarloh yaal ngo bele mmaechloh ire we, iwe yesa pungdiy molwe foloresal le yesa chuyloh molwe momayel. Be ila senger rechoka re mmal, bo rebe mes luwul yar yedamgel chog bo yebe palleng tot yar mmal.   
\s1 Hagilgil Mo Wegwegel Ladep  
\p
\v 12 Be momay depel semal le luwul yal weres ngo ye tugul chog lal depal bo be yoh ngali hagilgil le, ngo yebe yoh ngali molwe Deus ye hatugulu yebe fang ngalir rechokla re hachangi.  
\v 13 Hare yesa weweg depel semal ngo towe sor bo, “Wegwegel ladep le ila ye budoh mo irel Deus.” Bo towe yoh le moniyan yebe weged depel Deus, iwe ngo Deus ye tema weged depel yarmat ngal molfid.  
\v 14 Semal le bela weg depel ngo iy chog yal tagul sala mel luwul luluwal tayikof kala yal.  
\v 15 Iwe ngo luluwal tayikof la yal ila bele hasbudah molfid. Iwe ngo bela palleng loh molfid, ngo bele hasbudoh maes.   
\p
\v 16 Ha hafaelliy re wol bisiy bo rede kacheprahmi!  
\v 17 Pangal kkefang kala ye momay mo ikla ye kamdidiy, ngo ye bidiy mo wol laeng irel Deus we iy mele ye hasbu mekla hawerel laeng. Iy ila ye tema yusuwel igegal ngo ye tema tagul tang gich bo si dela mel luwul ruchupung.  
\v 18 Yal luluwal mele gich si subdoh mo luwul hapatpat la ye katos iyang, le sibe hamo mo imol pangal mekla ye hasbudoh.   
\s1 Hattaleng Mo Wegdeg  
\p
\v 19 Ha towe maligili mele re wol bisiy! Pangal yarmat ngo be cchang deper le rebe taelenga hapatpat, ngo rebe luluwal malulu ngo resa moch hapatpat, iwe ngo ye towe ma ttir chog yar ssong.  
\v 20 Ssong ila towe hasi ngalgich luluwal kala yael Deus le ye momay.  
\v 21 Ha hachuya wegdeg tayikof mo iremi. Ha tagul ngal Deus bo yebe yetolong hapatpat la ye momay lal mekla dipmi bo ila mala be yoh le yebe fang ngalugmi molow.   
\p
\v 22 Ha hafaeli bo de hami chog yami kacheprahmi, irel yami taelenga chog ngo ha temchael habe foru mekla yalol Deus.  
\v 23 Semal le yema hattaleng chog ngo ye tema mechael foru mekla yalol Deus, ila ye wochog semal le ye kalong lal pipiy ye sala wiri mala halngol igegal.  
\v 24 Yodla chog ye dartang pipiy we, ngo ye maliglaloh igegel molwe yongal.  
\v 25 Ngo semal le yebe chichiy hamayi hatobtob le ye hartael momay le yema hachuya fael molfid, iwe ngo yesa itol depal iyang, le towe mele chog yebe hataelenga bo yebe wol foru, ila ngo Deus yebe fang ngali yolbuw irel pangal mekla yema foru.   
\p
\v 26 Yor semal le ye luluwaley le ye itol depal irel yal tugul? Hare yebe te hafalliy mekla ye sosor, ngo tugul la yal ila tor pelal ngo yesa iy chog yal kekachepra.  
\v 27 Mala Deus le Temach ye sor bo halngol tugulul ladep ila iye: Ha hafallir yalwich ka tor wulutugur, mo fefel kala yesa mes rir le resa hafohoy, ngo hasa itol dipmi bo hade dabey wegdeg tayikof kala lal faileng le.   
\c 2  
\s1 Hobe Hafidgirloh Chog Panger Yarmat  
\p
\v 1 Re wol bisiy, luwul yami chepar irel Samol Jesus Kristus le iy mele Samolel falmay, ngo habe hafidgirloh chog panger yarmat. Ha towe hammal semal ngo hasa ligid semal bo yagel mekla igeger le ye llah mo lal metami.  
\v 2 Hare ye wochog bo semal mal le ye mmal ngo yor lol ring le hoal ngo ye momay mekla mengagol, ye budoh irel yami ttey, iwe ngo hare semal le ye hafohoy ngo ye ttar fedal mekla mengagol ye wol budoh,  
\v 3 hare yebe kkel yam hasrowu yeramtala ye momay mekla mengagol, ngo hosa kangalu bo, “Maro mo lobosle ye hartael momay” iwe ngo hosa kangalu mal we ye hafohoy bo, “Hola su mo iglay hare marodiy lal poa mo lengchel meka pechey,”  
\v 4 ila ngo hosa tayikof bo ho tay hafidgirloh yarmat, ngo mekla ho sor bo yarmat rebe foru ila ye budoh mo irel luluwal kala ye tayikof.   
\p
\v 5 Ha taelenga hami re wol bisiy! Deus ye duwler maelhafohoy ka lal faileng bo yebe kkel yar tugul, ngo ye yoh ngalir mala lamliyal le iy ye hatugulu yebe fang ngalir rechokla re hachangi.  
\v 6 Ngo hami hate hassaror maelhafohoy! Itey ir mekla rema hafohoyugmi ngo re hasugmiloh imor chol tatelal hapatpat? Rechokla re mmal!  
\v 7 Ir mele re kekatayikofa kaptael yidla ye momay le Deus ye fang ngalugmi.   
\p
\v 8 Hare habe dabey hatobtobol mala Lamliyel Deus ngo yebe fel yami mel, le iwe ye mel lal babior we ye santus we ye sor bo, “Ha hachangir yarmat le be wochog yami hachangugmi.”\x - \xo 2:8 \xt Lv 19:18\x*  
\v 9 Hare yebe kkel yami hassaror tot yarmat mo imor ikala tot le yagel chog mekla igeger le ha wiri, ila ngo hasa molfid ngo Hatobtob we be sor le hami hama hatawsi hatobtob.  
\v 10 Semal le ye hatawsi sew mo irel Hatobtob we, ngo yesa molfid irel yal hatawsi pangal loh.  
\v 11 Bo yeramtala ye sor bo, “Hami cho habulupoy ila ha towe faor maltemay ngal semal le te yami habulupoy.” Ngo wol iy chog mele ye sor bo, “Ha towe limeseloh semal.” Haramo hote foru ngal ril semal, ngo ho limeseloh semal ila ngo ho chil hatawsi chog hatobtob we.\x - \xo 2:11 \xt Ex 20:14; Dt 5:18; Ex 20:13; Dt 5:17\x*  
\v 12 Habe ma hapatpat ngo ha foru wegdegmi le be wochog rechokla Deus yebe hatugulu kofer le yebe dabey hatobtob we ye ma teladgich.  
\v 13 Bo Deus ila ye towe kawraloh yal ffahol ladep irel yodla yebe hatugulu kofer rechokla re tema fahor yarmat; iwe ngo ligdi bo ffahol ladep ila ye kkel mo imol hatugul.   
\s1 Tugulul Ladep Mo Wegdeg  
\p
\v 14 Re wol bisiy, meda mele kofael semal le ye sor bo yor yal tugulul ladep ngo yete llah mo irel wegdegel le ila sengal? Be yoh le tugul la yal be hadora?  
\v 15 Hare ye wochog bo yor tot bisbis hare mengeng le re hafohoy irel mengagur mo haler.  
\v 16 Meda mele mmaler mo irel mala hobe kangalur bo, “Deus ye be holbuwahmi! Ha hammal yami mel ngo ha hammal yami mongoy!” Le hare be tayichalmwo mele ha fang ngalir bo hammaler?  
\v 17 Ila wol ila sengal tugulul ladep: bo hare be iy chog llufulyal le be tamel wegdeg momay iyang, ila ngo ye mes.   
\p
\v 18 Yor semal le yebe sor bo, “Yor ikla yor yar tugul ngo yor ikla ye momay wegdigir.” Ngang ibe kangalugmi bo, “Habe kangaluyey hare be ifa sengal yal yor yael semal tugul ngo yete llah mo irel wegdegel, ila ngo ngang isa kkewar ngalugmi lepal yai tugul mo irel wegdegey.”  
\v 19 Ha chepar le ye halsemal Deus? Ye momay! Moniyan mwo ngo re wol chepar luwul kkelel yar motog.  
\v 20 Ha buch! Ha dipli le habe gola le tugulul ladep le be tor wegdeg momay iyang ngo tor kofal?  
\v 21 Ifa sengal chog ngo ye sala fel Abraham we chapdohoch mo irel Deus? Abraham ye kawraloh yal tugulul ladep ngal Deus mo irel yal wegdeg irel yodwe ye yetedah Isaac we lol wol altar we.\x - \xo 2:21 \xt Gn 22:1–14\x*  
\v 22 Ha ted medaf iyang? Yael Abraham tugulul ladep mo wegdeg ila sew chog. Tugulul ladep la yal ila yesa fel bo wegdegel ye dabey.  
\v 23 Iwe sala ppalungal mokwe babior we ye santus ye sor irel bo: “Abraham ye chepar ngal Deus, iwe ngo fael yal tugulul ladep mele Deus yesa foru bo yebe fel.” Iwe sala ffos idel Abraham le iy maryarel Deus.\x - \xo 2:23 \xt Gn 15:6; 2 Ch 20:7; Is 41:8\x*  
\v 24 Ila habe madefagili le yach wegdeg luwul yach tugulul ladep mele sima fel mo irel Deus iyang, ngo te yach chog tugulul ladep.   
\p
\v 25 Mele ila ye wochog molwe Rahab we iy semal fefel we yema tap chuway holngol ye foru. Luwul yal molfid ngo Deus ye hadora, bo yagel molwe ye hammaler saldawel Israel kowe ngo ye tipingir bo yebe yoh le rebe tefael ngalir mokwe choluwar.\x - \xo 2:25 \xt Js 2:1–21\x*   
\p
\v 26 Ila meka holngoch le yebe tamel meka nguluch iyang ngo yebe mes. Wol ila sengal tugulul ladep le yebe tor wegdeg momay iyang ngo yebe mes.   
\c 3  
\s1 Hapatpat  
\p
\v 1 Re wol bisiy, fedmal chog hami mele yebe mmal le rebe mel bo chol foloy. Hami ngo ha gola le hamem ika hasa mel bo chol foloy, ila Deus yebe halimchigi tot yal hatugulu kofmem mo imor sibis.  
\v 2 Pangach yarmat ngo sima machey. Iwe ngo hare semal le ye tema machey irel mekla yema kapta, ila ngo tor hapagol, ngo yebe wol yoh ngali le be iy chog yal haffaliy kofal llufulyal.  
\v 3 Sima hapanggiy sew mityel parang le yor yol lal yewal semal wos bo ila ngo yebe loh lobosle si dipli yebe loh iyang.  
\v 4 Ha luluwaley seyay barko. Heramo ye palleng ngo ye loloh luwul mmorol yaeng mo hatobtob, ngo halsew mityel fadol mele ye kekawele sa loloh lobola kapin we ye luluwaley be loh iyang.  
\v 5 Ila sengal mele yewach yarmat. Ye wechich ngo yema habos irel yal ma kapta hapatpat kala ye palleng.  
\p Habe luluwaley le sew mityel yaef ngo be yoh le yebe fisgaloh sew fuluy.  
\v 6 Mele yewach yarmat ila ye wochog sew yaef. Meka yewach ila madpil meka holngoch, ngo yal taiykof ila be yoh le yebe hatayikofagich. Yaef la yebe hasidoh mo Infiyerno, ila be yoh le yebe fisgaloh igegel yach memel.  
\v 7 Ye mmal ngal yarmat le rebe hafigerar pangal mael kala foruyel Deus: mael machoh, mael yeyal, mael kala rema mel wolfulu, ngo re wol ma mel leted mo yig.  
\v 8 Iwe ngo tor semal le ye yoh le yebe hafigra meka yewach yarmat. Mele ila sew tayikof le towe yoh sibe holu kofal. Iwe ngo yebe yoh le yebe lilimesloh yarmat, le be wochog semal parchoyoh kowe ye poison.  
\v 9 Sima tapeli meka yewach sibe kangalu Deus la Temach yal hachigchig. Iwe ngo sima wol tapeli sibe hapatpat tayikof irer rechokla Deus ye hasburdoh le re igegel iy Deus.\x - \xo 3:9 \xt Gn 1:26\x*  
\v 10 Hapatpat ka ye momay mo ika ye tayikof ila yema buyoy chog mo lal meka yewach yarmat. Re wol bisiy, mele ila towe iye sengal.  
\v 11 Tor sew chael le ha bela yid mo iyang le yebe lloay ngo ye wol merat.  
\v 12 Re wol bisiy, tor sehay \add fig\add* le bela buyoy uwal ngo ye bele uwal \add olives\add*. Towe yoh le yebe buyo \add grape\add* sala mel bo uwal \add fig\add*, ngo towe wol yoh le yebe budoh chael ka ye lloay mo irel sew chael le ye taed.   
\s1 Repiy La Ye Bidiy Mo Wol Laeng  
\p
\v 13 Yor semal mo luwulumi le ye teram ngo ye medaf lal depal? Semal le iy ngo yebe hallehaloh mo irel momayel yal wegdeg luwul malulu mo repiy.  
\v 14 Ngo hare lal mekla dipmi ila ye ssogol loltemay, mo luwalel chog holongmi llufulumi mo ssong, ila ngo ha towe foru bo habe molfid irel yami kachepar bo ha repiy.  
\v 15 Tappel repiy le ila yete bidiy mo wol laeng. Ye budoh mo wol talople iwe ngo te yael Espritu Santus, bo yael moniyan.  
\v 16 Solbos le yebe yor loltemay iyang ngo yarmat rema luluwaley chog kofer lufulyer, ila yebe wol yor taroprop mo pangal metmetael tayikof iyang.  
\v 17 Iwe ngo repiy la ye bidiy mo wol laeng ila tor derel. Ye pos, ngo ye malulu, ngo ye hakola, ngo ye ssogol ffaho mo wegdeg momay.  
\v 18 Ngo momay ila uwal milay kala rechokla rema hasidoh hopos rema fedagu luwul hopos.   
\c 4  
\s1 Hamareyar Ngal Faileng Le  
\p
\v 1 Iya lobosle yela budoh fedeg mo fedgel hapatpat kala yami mo iyang? Ye budoh mo irel mekla holongmi le pangal yad ngo yema hataropropa yami luluwal.  
\v 2 Ha chahawagili tot formel le towe yoh ngalugmi, iwe hasa lilimesloh yarmat. Ye kkel yami chahawagili tot formel, ngo ligdi bo towe yoh ngalugmi. Iwe hasa rol hachocho fengal ngo ha fedeg. Towe yoh ngalugmi mekla ha dipli bo ha tema dongor ngal Deus.  
\v 3 Iwe ngo ha bela dongor ngo towe yoh ngalugmi bo ye tayikof mekla ha luluwaley. Ha dongor formel bo habe taptap irel mekla yema momay dipmi iyang.  
\v 4 Yete tugul lal dipmi irel Deus. Ha gola le changel meka lal talop le ila ye happaliyel ngal Deus. Te tugul semal le ye dipli le yebe hammareyar ngal meka lal faileng le ngo yesa iy chog yal foru le yebe happaliyel ngal Deus.  
\v 5 Ha towe luluwaley le yete katos molwe ye mel lal babior we ye santus we ye sor bo, “Meka nguluch le Deus ye fang ngalgich, ila ye kkel yal cchang deper ngal Deus.”  
\v 6 Ngo ligdi bo ye kkel tot haradiya la Deus ye fang. Babior we ye santus ye sor bo, “Deus yema tagul tangir rechokla ye tagiyet yar luluwal, ngo yema fang haradiya ngalir ikla ye totol yar luluwal.”\x - \xo 4:6 \xt Pr 3:34 (LXX)\x*   
\p
\v 7 Ila ha taelenga yalol Deus. Ha fedeg ngal Moniyan bo ila ngo iy yebe ddar tangugmi.  
\v 8 Habe harpa Deus ngo iy Deus yebe harpahmi. Hami choto hamolfid, ha tela paomi! Ha taldi lal dipmi hami rechokla ha toa kachepar.  
\v 9 Habe harrig lal dipmi ngo hasa tang luwul yal tayikof dipmi. Habe liwli yami memal ngal tang, ngo hasa liwli yami rraey ngal tayikofel ladep!  
\v 10 Habe hatetalo yami luluwal mo fael metael Samol ngo iy yebe hatagitahmidah.   
\s1 Ha Towe Hapatpat Tayikof Irer Kristiano Kala Choluwami  
\p
\v 11 Hami re wol bisiy, ha towe hapatpat tayikof irel semal mo semal hami. Te tugul semal le ye hapatpat tayikof, hare ye hatugulu kofael semal Kristiano kala bisil, ila ngo iy yesa happaliyel ngal Hatobtob we ngo ye hatugulu kofal. Hare hobe hatugulu kofal Hatobtob we, ila ngo tay gel semal rechoka yema taelenga Hatobtob we, bo sa gel mele hobe hatugulu kofal.  
\v 12 Halachog Deus mele yema fang hatobtob, ngo iy chog mele yema hatugulu kofal. Iy chog llufulyal mele yebe yoh ngali le yebe hadorar yarmat hare ye limeserloh. Ha luluwaley ngo hami itey le habe hatugulu kofer mekla choluwami?   
\s1 Ha Towe Habos  
\p
\v 13 Ha taelengayey hami rechokla ha sor bo, “Igla hare walsu mele sibe loh irel haplom lay bo si bela melegili sew raeg, bo sibe yengangel salpiy bo yebe cholop salpiy le yebe yoh ngalgich.”\x - \xo 4:13 \xt 4:13–14; Pr 27:1\x*  
\v 14 Mala mwo yebe wel ngalugmi walsu ngo ha togla! Ha wochog burah kowe si wiriy ngo ye tema ssulay ngo ye moloh.  
\v 15 Far iye mele habe sor: “Hare depel Samol, ila ngo sibe molow bo sibe foru iye hare si foru ilay.”  
\v 16 Ngo ligdi bo igla ila hasa habos ngo ye tagiyet yami luluwal. Ye tabung le habe hatagitadah yami luluwal.   
\p
\v 17 Iwe ngo sew molfid mala semal yebe temchael foru mekla ye fel, le iy ngo ye gola le ye momay le yebe foru.   
\c 5  
\s1 Mekla Cho Mmal Re Towe Foru  
\p
\v 1 Ha taelenga hami rechokla ha mmal! Ha tang irel hafohoy kala bele holahmi!  
\v 2 Mmal ka yami ila yebe margoch loh ngo makla mengagmi ila maelcholap yebe hangiloh.\x - \xo 5:2 \xt 5:2–3; Mt 6:19\x*  
\v 3 Hoal mo silver kala lomi ila yebe yew loh, ngo ila mele yebe mel le tugulul mala ha chehaw ngo ha tayikof; ngo yebe llugmi loh le be wochog bo ha fisngeg loh irel yaef. Ye cholop mmalmi le hasa hateyli irel ral ka yesa hartael ral.  
\v 4 Ha tede fang paliyer rechokla rema yengang irel milay kala yami. Ha taelenga mekla re sosor bo hami ha tayikof iyang. Mekla yalor chol yengang kala rema hateyili fengali uwal milay kala yami ila yesa hola Deus le iy Samol le pangal ngo yema yoh irel.\x - \xo 5:4 \xt Dt 24:14–15\x*  
\v 5 Ha mel wol talop le, le luwul mmal mo mekla yema momay dipmi iyang. Hasa habdayugmi le fal ngal ralla rebe llugmi habe mes.  
\v 6 Hasa hatugulu yar hagerger rechokla tor mele re hadre ngo ha limeserloh, ngo ir rete fedeg ngalugmi.   
\s1 Malulu Mo Mepel  
\p
\v 7 Hami rewol bisiy, habe yedamgel chog luwul malulu yee, la hola yodla yebe budoh Samol iyang. Ha kemahoy yar malulu chol milay irel yar wiwidi yodla yebe yor uwal milay kala yar le ye palleng fal ngalir. Rema widi mala metamol ppotog mo mala hartael ppotog luwul yar malulu.  
\v 8 Ila hami habe wol malulu. Ha hakela dipmi bo ralla yebe budoh Samol iyang ila yesa harep.   
\p
\v 9 Hami rewol bisiy, ha towe ma rol ssong fengal, ila ngo Deus towe hatugulu kofmi. Chol Tatelal Hapatpat we ila yesa harep le yebe budoh.  
\v 10 Hami rewol bisiy, ha memangi chog profeta kowe re kapatpat le fael idel Samol. Ha kay mo irer wululul yar malulu mo lepal kelel lal deper irel hafohoy kowe ye holar.  
\v 11 Gich si sor bo re rraey bo fael mala ye kel yar yedamgel. Hasa moal rongrong kofael Job irel yal yedamgel luwul malulu, ngo ha gola we la wol miril loh ngo Samol ye tipingi. Bo Samol ila ye ffaho depal ngo ye momay yal hagiyeg.\x - \xo 5:11 \xt Job 1:2–22; 2:10; Ps 103:8\x*   
\p
\v 12 Hami rewol bisiy, ye palleng fal le ha towe teptap mala idel Deus irel yami hatugulu sew formel ngal semal le habe foru. Ha towe hatugulu sew formel le habe teptap mala idel laeng hare talop hare te tugul sew formel. Ha sor bo, “Ngoa” hare ila sengal yami luluwal. Ha sor bo “Yeb” hare ila sengal yami luluwal. Ila ngo Deus towe fang yami hagerger.\x - \xo 5:12 \xt Mt 5:34–37\x*   
\p
\v 13 Yor semal hami igla le yesa hafohoy? Ye momay le yebe mepel. Yor semal le ye rraey? Ye momay le be tonel hapingping.  
\v 14 Yor semal hami le ye tomay? Ye momay le yebe dengag mal kala yar yarmetael eklesia rebe budoh irel bo rebe mepel uwol ngo re chalfi ngal hapgep fael mala idel Samol.\x - \xo 5:14 \xt Mk 6:13\x*  
\v 15 Mapel la rebe foru luwul tugul ila yebe hachuya yael yeramtawe tomay. Samol ye be hachuya yal tomay, ngo molfid kowe yesa foru ila yebe chuy.  
\v 16 Ha telad fengali molfid kala hasa foru ngo hasa hasi yael semal mo semal hami mepel, ila ngo be chuy yami tomay. Rechokla re momay ila ye palleng kamelal yar mapel.  
\v 17 Elijah ila ye hafedeg ngalgich chog. Ye kel yal mapela bo ye towe ppotog, ngo yete ppotog wulfulu irel suluw mo setab raeg.\x - \xo 5:17 \xt 1 K 17:1; 18:1\x*  
\v 18 Ngo yesa wol mepel fael sew ngo yesa ppotog sa tumul fedah ye sala yor uwal.\x - \xo 5:18 \xt 1 K 18:42–45\x*   
\p
\v 19 Hami rewol bisiy, hare semal hami yesa tahchaloh meka ye katos, ngo semal hami yesa loh bo ye bela hatefalidoh.  
\v 20 Iwe ngo ha towe maligili mele: Samol le yebe hatefaeli semal choto hamolfid le sa hachuya mo luwul tayikof kala yesa foforu, ila ngo iy yesa hadora molwe ngul choto hamolfid we mo irel maes. Ila ngo yebe cholop molfid le yebe chuy.\x - \xo 5:20 \xt Pr 10:12; 1 P 4:8\x*   